data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home that is ready for you! When you walk through the front door you will be met by a spacious entry foyer. The beautiful LVP floors throughout the home showcase the already beautiful natural light. The kitchen overlooks the living room making sure you are always connected with your family! The spacious living room is great for entertaining guests, but also perfect for you to enjoy quality family time. When you walk onto the back patio, you will notice how large your lot is and can be turned into your own oasis! This backyard allows you to enjoy the possibility of a fire-pit or hot tub, while letting your pets run free!
